<br>
  Reason here is simple. /follow is a DIRECT LINE to your target, no matter what is in your way. That means, lava, water, tree, mountain, whatnot will block your path, and you will not path around it to continue following. Also, if the obstacle in your way is lethal, you will die while on autofollow.<br>
<br>
  Now, what gets me is that in places where Pet has Line of Sight to it's master, why can the pet not go direct? That's a fscking straight line, it shouldn't take a path just to find it's target. now, if the pet has no LoS to you, then it resorts back to the Path system, or if you're too far away, or whatnot. This would negate the need for paths in many open areas, and permit easy 'leading' of your pet to where you want to go. This would also negate the issues of send the pet in, watch as it nagivates half the zone to get to it's destination, so long as you (and the pet) have a direct LoS to the target.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umagnomightymidget.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MagnoMightymidget</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#333333>(12/12/01 9:09:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=47.topic&index=36>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   RE: Easy</span><hr size=1> Well I sent an e-mail off to eqtech@soe.sony.com.  Now I'm just crossing my fingers that they will read and accept it. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/udisputatiousdeathmage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Disputatious Deathmage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#333333>(12/13/01 12:43:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=47.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: RE: Easy