And when you lose a pet you don't just lose the 50 mana or whatever due to reclaim energy...unless you're an idiot and don't usebuffs: burnout (175 mana), dmg shield (150 mana), new armors (not sure how much but it's a lot). Well right there just adding up those 3 spells is over 400 mana. You don't JUST lose that 400 for casting the pet. It is not mana efficient or group efficient to have to resummon a pet every time you move. It takes about 30 seconds or more to resummon a pet and rebuff it also. <p>
